O Abu Lahab

00:48:13.510 --> 00:48:18.340
a total destruction

00:48:18.340 --> 00:48:20.540
his wealth will not help him in any way

00:48:20.540 --> 00:48:21.440
nothing

00:48:21.440 --> 00:48:23.840
his wealth did not assist him or help him

00:48:23.840 --> 00:48:25.940
neither in his life nor in his death

00:48:25.940 --> 00:48:29.140
because that is the Quranic injunction

00:48:29.140 --> 00:48:31.440
